headline: Analog Devices (ADI): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Analog Devices has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 18.2% to $275.75 per share while the index has gained 13.4%.
